The paper proposes a method for automatically generating summaries for scientific papers, which involves utilizing videos of talks at scientific conferences. This task involves natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR) techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.CL and cs.IR. The paper also mentions the use of machine learning models, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.DL. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
